webResources.textAttributionSnippet: (en) The Great Hotel in Lköpping from a time before the hotel was built with one floor. In the hotel’s ground plan, shops were run, most closely to Frans Wilhelm Österberg’s clothing store followed by Johan Conrad Krouthén’s manual shop. The building was built in 1852 after drawings by Jonas Jonsson - https://www.europeana.eu/item/73/S_OM_photo_OMEA0001240119. Östergötlands museum - http://digitaltmuseum.se/021017433161. Public Domain Mark - http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/mark/1.0/
